This was a fun thing to do on the side, with IRL stuff for me being so busy lately. DrBleep did most of this, then I came in and rewrote the meta collapsibles.

I should say, as a disclaimer - some people might take away from this that we're against the Grand Crosslinking (Operation Flat Horizon). We're very much not - I love the idea of making canon more cohesive and interconnected. The perspectives of the characters on the ground don't represent us, here.







